-- Jefferies Hires Two Bankers From ING to Boost Fixed-Income Sales in France
-- Paul Dobson
-- 2010-06-21T08:15:56Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-21/jefferies-hires-two-bankers-from-ing-to-boost-fixed-income-sales-in-france.html

          
          
             Jefferies International Ltd. said it
hired two bankers from ING Groep NV to expand rates sales in
France.  
 Jefferies hired Marie-Laure Savelli-Timsit  as a managing
director and head of rates sales in France, and  Maxim-Alexandre Simon  as a vice-president for rates sales, it said today in an
e-mailed statement.  
